# shacdn ‚Äî reuse outside this repo

When the user ports or consumes **shacdn** UI primitives in another React + Vite (or SPA) project:

1. Read **`docs/INTEGRATION_GUIDE.md`** first ‚Äî quick start, deps, Vite/Next.js, checklist.
2. Prefer **shacdn MCP** tools (`get_integration_guide`, `get_design_system`, `get_component_bundle`) ‚Äî see `.cursor/rules/shacdn-mcp.mdc`.
3. Pick controls: **`docs/COMPONENTS_AI_REFERENCE.md`** (task ‚Üí component), then **`docs/STYLE_GUIDE.md`** (tokens, patterns).
4. Copy **`src/styles/globals.scss`** and **`variables.scss`** before individual components.
5. Copy component folders **whole** (tsx + module.scss); respect internal deps (Modal‚ÜíDialog, DatePicker‚ÜíCalendar, etc.).
6. For landing layouts, use **`get_screen_pattern("sessy-landing")`** or mirror **`src/screens/SessyLanding/`**.
7. After edits in the consumer project: **`npm run lint`** and **`npm run build`**.
